extendedInfo.description: Save grocery coupons to your grocery savings card. They're automatically applied at checkout! Works at over 25 US grocers including Kroger, ShopRite, and Giant Eagle (limited avail. in NYC, FL, MA).

reviews.title: Useful if your grocery store supports it
reviews.comment: I don\'t know why people are 1-starring this just because they can\'t use it with their grocery store. Not all services work with all choices, and it\'s unrealistic to expect them to. It\'s a shame if you can\'t use it, it really is, but bogging down the app\'s score with complaints not about the app but the service isn\'t going to help them grow and expand to more stores.  In the meantime, it supports Kroger, and there are tons of those near me, so I\'m a happy user.
